87 void testSBC_TriggerWatchdogIfRequired(void) {
88  TEST_ASSERT_FALSE(TEST_SBC_TriggerWatchdogIfRequired(&sbc_stateMcuSupervisor));
89  sbc_stateMcuSupervisor.watchdogTrigger = 10u;
90  /* decrement so we are going to see a trigger event */
91  for (int i = 0; i < sbc_stateMcuSupervisor.watchdogPeriod_10ms - 1; i++) {
92  TEST_ASSERT_FALSE(TEST_SBC_TriggerWatchdogIfRequired(&sbc_stateMcuSupervisor));
93  }
94  /* timer has elapsed now, we should see a trigger event */
95  SBC_TriggerWatchdog_IgnoreAndReturn(STD_OK);
96  TEST_ASSERT_TRUE(TEST_SBC_TriggerWatchdogIfRequired(&sbc_stateMcuSupervisor));
97  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(sbc_stateMcuSupervisor.watchdogTrigger, sbc_stateMcuSupervisor.watchdogPeriod_10ms);
98 
99  /* elapse timer and fail to run watchdog trigger */
100  sbc_stateMcuSupervisor.watchdogTrigger = 1u;
101  SBC_TriggerWatchdog_IgnoreAndReturn(STD_NOT_OK);
102  TEST_ASSERT_FALSE(TEST_SBC_TriggerWatchdogIfRequired(&sbc_stateMcuSupervisor));
103 }
